      "width": 560,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Legend / Type Selector Smoke\n\nThis graph exposes visible node-class bridges and edge-class ports together.\n\nUse it to check that:\n\n- legend shows the same visible vocabulary selectors use\n- markdown is still available by courtesy\n- bridge-backed creation is real\n- tagged edges pick up edge-class meaning and render defaults",
