      "width": 520,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# How To Use\n\n1. Open the Legend panel and confirm the bridge entries appear.\n2. Use a selector or legend spawn action to create from a visible bridge.\n3. Confirm markdown is still exposed.\n4. Inspect the sample edges below and confirm `edgeClassKey` values match the edge-class ports.\n5. Confirm the tagged edges render through the linked edge classes.",
